No short snort will suit me, jack.
Long, strong, and consecutive; 
Hold me close like aces back to back.

Kiss me sweet, smooth, and conclusively; 
No weak squeak--get on the beam.
Kiss me sweet, and conclusively, 
Got to be good to be on my home team.

